    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 128.</p><p>Killing Winds</p><p>10th-level necromancy</p><p>Classes: Cleric, Warlock Casting Time: 1 action Range: 500 feet Components: V, S, M (the carcass of an infernal locust and the favor of a deity) Duration: Instantaneous</p><p>A powerful wind lifts from a point you choose within range, and with it, the last breath of all mortals. Creatures with less than 100 hit points in a 100-footradius sphere centered on that point die instantly, dropping limp where they stand. Creatures with more than 100 hit points must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or die instantly. The wind violently swings open doors and windows and extinguishes open flames, but affects no other physical entities. Creatures surrounded by at least 10 feet of solid matter are not affected by this spell.</p></div>",
